## Ok, but what _IS_ `Quarto`®?

![](images/quarto-confused-short.jpg){style="position: absolute; top: 250; left: 20px; width: 1300px;" alt-text="A tweet by Erwin Lares: #RStats can someone explain to me what's the difference between Quarto and RMarkdown. I saw a tweet about Quarto and now I'm all confused ... What gap is it supposed to fill?"}





## Ok, but what _IS_ `Quarto`®?

> [Quarto® is an open-source scientific and technical publishing system built on Pandoc]{style="font-size:80px;"}

. . .

:::{style="font-size: 75px;"}
```bash
pandoc -s MANUAL.txt -o example2.html
```
:::

. . .

:::{style="font-size: 75px;"}
```lua
function Strong(elem)
  return pandoc.SmallCaps(elem.c)
end
```
:::
. . .

:::{style="font-size: 75px;"}

```bash
quarto publish document.qmd
```

:::

