## Cocktails vs Mixed Drinks

::: r-stack
![](images/mixed-drink.jpg){.fragment width="800px" fig-align="left" alt-text="A tweet by Mara Averick. The tweet is a bunny shaking a shaker and then holding a martini glass. The bunny says 'this is just a mixed drink'"}

![](images/cocktail-kuhn.jpg){.fragment width="1200px" fig-align="left" alt-text="A Tweet by Max Kuhn: There is a growing schism in the tidyverse group about the difference between a cocktail and a mixed drink. The official tidyverse opinion is that a **cocktail is made with love and care**. I assume that a mixed drink is then a lazy, unholy coupling between ingredients and alcohol."}
